<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BrightStar/login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <!-- link to fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- link to icons -->
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <a href="/" class="Logo">Bright<span>Star</span></a>
            <div class="buttons-list">
                <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="login-register__block">
            <form action="/login" method="post">
                <h1>Авторизація</h1>
                <input type="text" name="login" id="login" placeholder="Введіть логін...">
                <input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Введіть пароль...">
                <p>{{message}}</p>
                <p>Ще не маєете акаунта? <a href="/register">Зарегеструватись</a></p>
                <button type="submit">Увійти</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script src="js/srcipt.js"></script>
</body>
</html>